      "updated": 1777605626594,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Link creation\n  -> short-code\n  -> custom-link\n\nLinks stats\n  -> Total clicks\n  -> Avg. Clicks\n  -> Active links\n  -> Node uptime\n\nNetwork Traffic\n  -> whole week traffic\n    \n\nTop Performer\n   -> sort by week, months, 3 months\n   -> items includes link name with link url\n   -> clicks\n   -> avg clicks \n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Link creation\n  -> short-code\n  -> custom-link\n\nLinks stats\n  -> Total clicks\n  -> Avg. Clicks\n  -> Active links\n  -> Node uptime\n\nNetwork Traffic\n  -> whole week traffic\n    \n\nTop Performer\n   -> sort by week, months, 3 months\n   -> items includes link name with link url\n   -> clicks\n   -> avg clicks \n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
